<paragraph id="39642141FFC5FFB5FF6BFF4AFC6FFE01" blockId="5.[174,1233,175,490]" pageId="5" pageNumber="184">
C o m p a r a t i v e n o t e s. Based on the similar morphology of the male primary and secondary sexual characters 
<taxonomicName id="FEDB5AC2FFC5FFB5FE7DFEAAFC86FEA2" authority="Glotov" authorityName="Glotov" authorityYear="2014" box="[501,846,271,297]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Gyrophaena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="184" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plutenkoi" status="sp. n.">
